Beat it.

76
00:03:51,823 --> 00:03:52,789
Uh-oh.

77
00:03:52,824 --> 00:03:53,824
Ah!

78
00:03:53,858 --> 00:03:56,727
Oh, ah!

79
00:03:56,761 --> 00:03:59,129
