I don't know what you're talking about.

114
00:05:54,752 --> 00:05:57,253
听着，士兵，不管你的任务是什么
Listen to me, soldier,
whatever your assignment is,

115
00:05:57,288 --> 00:05:59,288
也不可能比我的任务重要
it can't be more important than mine.

116
00:05:59,323 --> 00:06:01,057
这是他第一次真正的任务
It is his first real mission.

117
00:06:01,091 --> 00:06:02,725
他只是一个读图员
He is just a map reader.

118
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:05,261
别听那个笨蛋的话
Don't listen to that ignoramus.

119
00:06:05,295 --> 00:06:08,897
你是一个克隆人，也是一个共和国军队里面的士兵
You are a clone and a soldier
in the Republic Army,

120
00:06:08,932 --> 00:06:11,533
我命令你带我上你的飞船
and I order you to take me to your ship.

121
00:06:11,567 --> 00:06:14,236
