Uh, look, friend,
I was just trying to help.

123
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:19,241
如果你不误人子弟就好了
I'm sorry if you took it the wrong way.

124
00:06:19,275 --> 00:06:20,575
我想那个士兵
I do not think that soldier

125
00:06:20,610 --> 00:06:24,179
不相信你也是一个克隆，嗯，上校
believes you are a colonel, uh, Colonel.

126
00:06:24,214 --> 00:06:25,514
Gregor!

127
00:06:25,548 --> 00:06:27,783
干活去吧
Get back to work.

128
00:06:27,817 --> 00:06:30,085
嗯，对不起，我必须走了
Uh, excuse me.
I got to go.

129
00:06:30,119 --> 00:06:32,354
我不想失去我的工作
I don't want to lose my job.

130
00:06:34,791 --> 00:06:37,626
