Well, what's the scouting report?

134
00:06:52,675 --> 00:06:56,344


135
00:06:56,379 --> 00:06:57,846
分离势力的铁皮人？
Separatist droids?

136
00:06:57,913 --> 00:07:01,483
嗯，那会让事情复杂化
Hmm, well, that complicates matters.

137
00:07:04,086 --> 00:07:07,655
这样，嗯，老板
So, uh, boss,

138
00:07:07,690 --> 00:07:09,391
你知道，我有个疑问...
you know, I was just wondering...

139
00:07:09,425 --> 00:07:12,493
不，你得不到升职,Gregor
No, you can't have a raise, Gregor.

140
00:07:12,528 --> 00:07:13,628
哦，不 不 不 不 
Oh, no, no, no, no.

141
00:07:13,662 --> 00:07:15,663
我不是想升职，先生
I don't want a raise, sir.

142
00:07:15,698 --> 00:07:19,534
我-我只是想，克隆人是什么？
I-I just wanted to know,
what's a clone?

143
00:07:19,568 --> 00:07:22,304
有人告诉我，我是一个克隆人
Someone told me I was a clone today.

144
00:07:22,338 --> 00:07:23,405
他们很确信这点
They insisted.

145
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:24,606
嗯，一个克隆人？
Heh.
A clone?

146
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,707


147
00:07:25,741 --> 00:07:29,043
克隆人在星系间战斗
Clones fight battles across the galaxy.

148
00:07:29,078 --> 00:07:31,213
他们是勇敢的战士
They are brave soldiers.

149
00:07:31,247 --> 00:07:34,582
你和他们有何相似之处？
Does that sound like you?

150
00:07:34,616 --> 00:07:37,084
你是一个洗碗工，Gregor.
You're a dishwasher, Gregor.

151
00:07:37,119 --> 00:07:40,788
忘了克隆人或相关事情
Forget about clones
or anything like that.

152
00:07:40,822 --> 00:07:42,990
