But I thought
maybe you could--

159
00:07:53,467 --> 00:07:55,835
能不能告诉我，我是怎么到这儿的？
could you tell me, how did I get here?

160
00:07:55,869 --> 00:07:57,003
你在哪里找到我的？
Where did you find me?

161
00:07:57,037 --> 00:07:58,404
