and commandeer that shuttle
without incident.

187
00:09:24,056 --> 00:09:26,391


188
00:09:26,425 --> 00:09:27,859
铁皮人有个想法，上校
The 'mechs have a point, Colonel.

189
00:09:27,893 --> 00:09:29,494
自从我们上次战舰行动以后
After what we did on the dreadnought,

190
00:09:29,528 --> 00:09:32,630
