00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:38,135
嗯，你们铁皮人可能有自己的看法
Hmm, you droids may have a point.

193
00:09:38,169 --> 00:09:39,870
但没有捷径可走
But there's no way in Malachor

194
00:09:39,904 --> 00:09:42,739
我准备带领这支可怜的小分队
that I'm going to lead
this pitiful squad

195
00:09:42,773 --> 00:09:45,341
对那个着陆点进行一次攻击
on an assault of that landing zone.

196
00:09:45,376 --> 00:09:46,943
上校，你有什么计划？
What is the plan now, Colonel?

197
00:09:46,977 --> 00:09:51,013
我要等到我们的克隆人下班
We're going to wait
until our clone gets off work,

198
00:09:51,048 --> 00:09:55,051
才能取得他的帮助，不管他愿不愿意
then enlist his help,
whether he wants to or not.

199
00:10:27,250 --> 00:10:28,617


200
