REX上尉报到
Captain Rex reporting for duty.

201
00:10:49,305 --> 00:10:50,705
啊！什么？
Agh! What?

202
00:10:56,979 --> 00:10:58,679
我...
I...

203
00:10:58,713 --> 00:11:00,247
我不明白
I don't understand.

204
00:11:00,281 --> 00:11:02,515
