That's me?

205
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:04,617
不，那是REX上尉
No, that's Captain Rex.

206
00:11:04,652 --> 00:11:07,286
他是共和国军队的克隆人士兵
He's a clone in the Republic Army,

207
00:11:07,321 --> 00:11:09,455
就像你一样，Gregor.
just like you, Gregor.

208
00:11:09,489 --> 00:11:13,158
真不敢相信
I can't believe it.

209
00:11:13,193 --> 00:11:14,793
OK, 别急，放松
Okay, slow down.
Slow down.

210
00:11:14,827 --> 00:11:19,365
你是说还有更多这样的克隆人？
So you're telling me that there
are more of these clones?

211
00:11:19,399 --> 00:11:22,301
数以百万。整个军队都是
Millions.
A whole army's worth.

212
00:11:22,335 --> 00:11:24,036
Uh-huh.

213
00:11:24,071 --> 00:11:27,373
他们看起来和我一模一样？
And they all look exactly like me?

214
00:11:27,408 --> 00:11:30,876
不，那些克隆人都是战士，
No, those clones are warriors,

215
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:33,912
由共和国创造的职业军人，
professional soldiers
created by the Republic,

216
00:11:33,947 --> 00:11:37,182
训练有素，勇敢无畏
trained to fight, and die if necessary,

217
00:11:37,217 --> 00:11:39,618
在我们对抗分离势力的战争中建功立业
in our war against the Separatists.

218
00:11:39,652 --> 00:11:40,986
他们不是在害虫出没的洞穴中
They're not dishwashers

219
00:11:41,020 --> 00:11:44,389
生活的洗碗工。
living in
some vermin-infested hovel.

220
00:11:44,423 --> 00:11:46,158


221
00:11:46,192 --> 00:11:49,328
听着，能在这里生活，我觉得很幸运
Look, I'm lucky to live in this place.

222
00:11:49,362 --> 00:11:52,364
博克斯先生说我的薪水不包括房租
Mr. Borkus says my salary
doesn't even cover the rent,

223
00:11:52,398 --> 00:11:54,265
他对我特殊优待
so he pays the difference for me.

224
00:11:54,300 --> 00:11:55,967
难道你不明白，Gregor?
Don't you get it, Gregor?

225
00:11:56,002 --> 00:11:57,469
你是他的奴隶
You're his slave.

226
00:11:57,503 --> 00:11:59,671
我们需要找到你的归属
We need to figure out
who you really are,

227
00:11:59,739 --> 00:12:01,273
你如何来到这里
how you got here.

228
00:12:01,308 --> 00:12:04,376
你确定你不能记起任何事情？
Are you sure
you don't remember anything?

229
00:12:04,411 --> 00:12:10,483
嗯，我记得我在一辆运输船上醒来
Well, all I remember is
waking up on a transport.

230
00:12:10,517 --> 00:12:12,685
因为某种原因我们坠毁在ABAFAR星球
Somehow we crashed on Abafar.

231
00:12:12,719 --> 00:12:16,956
还有，博克斯先生说我有健忘症
And, well, Mr. Borkus says
I have amnesia.

232
00:12:17,023 --> 00:12:18,223
嗯
Hmm.

233
00:12:18,258 --> 00:12:21,760
每个克隆人手腕上都有识别码
Every clone has an
identifying code on their wrist.

234
00:12:21,794 --> 00:12:24,429
你在军队服役的记录都在数据库里面
Your military records
will be in the database.

235
00:12:24,464 --> 00:12:25,864
扫描他，R2
Scan him, Artoo.

236
00:12:25,899 --> 00:12:27,299


237
