真令人吃惊，
Impressive.

238
00:12:35,076 --> 00:12:40,748
Gregor, 你的型号是CC-5576-39.
your designation
is CC-5576-39.

239
00:12:40,782 --> 00:12:45,286
你曾在一支精英小分队里服役，上尉军衔
You were a captain
and part of an elite squad.

240
00:12:45,321 --> 00:12:47,589
一个克隆人指挥官
A clone commando.

241
00:12:47,623 --> 00:12:49,458


242
00:12:49,492 --> 00:12:51,259
你的资料显示
Your file says you were reported

243
00:12:51,294 --> 00:12:53,795
你在一次战斗中失踪
missing in action during

244
00:12:53,863 --> 00:12:55,630
萨里斯战役
the Battle of Sarrish.

245
00:12:55,665 --> 00:12:56,965


246
00:12:56,999 --> 00:12:59,434
萨里斯?

247
00:12:59,502 --> 00:13:01,436
萨里斯.

248
00:13:01,470 --> 00:13:03,538
等一下

249
00:13:03,572 --> 00:13:05,773
萨里斯战役是什么？
What was the Battle of Sarrish?

250
00:13:05,808 --> 00:13:09,677
它是共和国军队损失惨重的战役之一
It was one of the Republic's
most devastating losses.

251
00:13:09,712 --> 00:13:12,046
萨里斯战役

252
00:13:12,081 --> 00:13:13,715
是的
Yes.

253
00:13:13,749 --> 00:13:15,717
是的，我记起来了
Yes, I remember now.

254
00:13:15,784 --> 00:13:18,186
很多士兵死亡
So many soldiers were dying.

255
00:13:18,220 --> 00:13:21,590
你记得你是如何逃离萨里斯战役的吗？
Dodo you remember
how you escaped Sarrish?

256
00:13:23,426 --> 00:13:24,693
记不起了
No.

257
00:13:24,727 --> 00:13:28,998
我只记得一眼望去全是尸体
I just remember seeing all those bodies.

258
00:13:29,032 --> 00:13:31,500
漫山遍野的尸体
Bodies everywhere.

259
00:13:31,535 --> 00:13:33,402
我只记得我必须寻求帮助
I knew I had to get help.

260
00:13:33,437 --> 00:13:36,606
但记忆就在这里中断了
But that's where the memory stops.

261
00:13:36,641 --> 00:13:37,941
好吧，士兵
Well, soldier,

262
00:13:37,976 --> 00:13:41,244
现在你对那场战役也帮不上什么忙
there's nothing you can do
about that battle now,

263
00:13:41,279 --> 00:13:42,379
但你能帮助我们
but you can help us.

264
00:13:42,413 --> 00:13:43,380


265
00:13:43,415 --> 00:13:45,349
我们的任务全靠它了
Our mission depends on it.

266
00:13:52,391 --> 00:13:55,793
嗯，上校，Gregor刚才说给他5分钟考虑
Uh, Colonel, Gregor said
to give him five minutes,

267
00:13:55,827 --> 00:13:57,528
但现在已经6分钟了
but it has been six.

268
00:13:57,563 --> 00:13:59,831
如果他不愿意加入我们怎么办？
What if he does not accept
your offer to join us?

269
00:13:59,865 --> 00:14:01,333
那么我会回到那儿
Then I'll go back in there

270
00:14:01,367 --> 00:14:04,036
亲自灌输一些理念给他
and personally
knock some sense into him.

271
00:14:04,070 --> 00:14:05,037
那没必要吧
That won't be necessary.

272
00:14:05,071 --> 00:14:06,238
Whoa!

273
00:14:06,272 --> 00:14:07,639


274
00:14:07,674 --> 00:14:09,608
让我的外表看起来象一个士兵
I figured
at least looking like a soldier

275
00:14:09,642 --> 00:14:11,710
也许能带回更多的记忆
might bring back some more memories,

276
00:14:11,744 --> 00:14:13,912
不管怎样，首先要找回我的装备
until we recover my equipment anyway.

277
00:14:13,947 --> 00:14:16,115
我听到你们这些家伙的谈话
I overheard you guys talking.

278
00:14:16,149 --> 00:14:18,383
我想我知道我的武器在哪了
I think I know where my armor is.

279
00:14:18,418 --> 00:14:19,818
让我们检查一下餐厅
Let's go check out the diner.

280
00:14:29,195 --> 00:14:31,864
动起来，士兵们。这不是舞会
Step it up, soldiers.
This isn't a party.

281
00:14:31,898 --> 00:14:33,832
我们没有整晚的时间
We do not have all night.

282
00:14:37,103 --> 00:14:38,737
再找这个？
Looking for this?

283
00:14:43,776 --> 00:14:47,544
我的制服  我的装备
My uniform.
My equipment.

284
00:14:47,579 --> 00:14:50,614
一直以来你都知道我是谁，而不告诉我
All this time you knew who I was
and didn't tell me.

285
00:14:50,649 --> 00:14:51,615
为什么？
Why?

286
00:14:51,650 --> 00:14:54,785
我不在乎你是谁
I don't care who you were.

287
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:56,687
你现在就是洗碗工
You are dishwasher now.

288
00:14:56,722 --> 00:15:00,793
而且是我把你从坠毁事故中救出来
And you owe me for saving you
from your crash.

289
00:15:00,827 --> 00:15:03,396
你的命是我的，Gregor.
Your life is mine, Gregor.

290
00:15:03,430 --> 00:15:05,164
你没有救我
You didn't save me.

291
00:15:05,198 --> 00:15:07,199
你把我变成一个奴隶
You turned me into a slave.

292
00:15:07,234 --> 00:15:09,702
我一直在这个垃圾场工作，听你发号施令
I've worked in this dump
taking orders from you

293
00:15:09,736 --> 00:15:11,637
本来我应该为共和国而去战斗
when I could have been fighting
for the Republic.

294
00:15:11,672 --> 00:15:13,239
我要恢复我自己的生活
I want my life back.

295
00:15:13,307 --> 00:15:15,608
你想要你的自由，Gregor？
You want your freedom, Gregor?

296
00:15:15,642 --> 00:15:17,877
从我这里拿起你的枪
Take your gun from me.

297
00:15:17,945 --> 00:15:20,246
向我展示一下你是一个士兵
Show me you are a soldier.

298
00:15:20,313 --> 00:15:21,413


299
00:15:21,448 --> 00:15:22,748
明白了吗？
You see?

300
00:15:22,782 --> 00:15:25,050
你不再是士兵
You are no soldier.

301
00:15:25,085 --> 00:15:27,152
你是一个洗碗工
You are a dishwasher.

302
00:15:35,728 --> 00:15:38,564
啊，你们这些破铜烂铁
Why, you no-good droids.

303
00:15:38,598 --> 00:15:41,800
放开我
Let go of me.

304
00:15:41,835 --> 00:15:43,069
Agh! Oh.

305
00:15:44,104 --> 00:15:45,537
Agh!

306
00:15:45,572 --> 00:15:47,539
拿上你的东西，Gregor.
Take your things, Gregor.

307
00:15:47,573 --> 00:15:48,941
我们一起离开这里
We're getting out of here.

308
00:15:51,645 --> 00:15:53,345
别走，Gregor.
Don't leave, Gregor.

309
00:15:53,380 --> 00:15:55,647
外面是浩渺无限的星系
It's a big galaxy out there,

310
00:15:55,682 --> 00:15:57,149
比你想象的还要大
bigger than you know.

311
00:15:57,184 --> 00:16:00,152
留下来，你的生活很简单
Stay here, where your life is simple.

312
00:16:00,187 --> 00:16:02,755
对这个克隆人来说
Simple isn't good enough anymore.

313
00:16:02,789 --> 00:16:04,423
简单不再美好了
Not for this clone.

314
00:16:04,457 --> 00:16:05,424
Ha!

315
00:16:05,458 --> 00:16:07,993
你永远不能离开ABAFAR
You will never get off Abafar,

316
00:16:08,061 --> 00:16:11,397
你和你的这些共和国朋友都如此
you and your little Republic friends,

317
00:16:11,431 --> 00:16:14,767
你们的绝地巡逻舰爆炸之后就注定了
not after your Jedi cruiser blows up.

318
00:16:14,801 --> 00:16:16,936
你究竟在讲什么？
What are you talking about?

319
00:16:16,970 --> 00:16:21,241
你认为分离势力为什么来这里？
Why do you think the
Separatists bother coming here?

320
00:16:21,275 --> 00:16:23,243
他们正在挖矿，名叫Rhydonium
They are mining our Rhydonium

321
00:16:23,277 --> 00:16:26,513
把矿物装上自己的飞船，然后破坏你们的巡逻舰
to load on the shuttle
and destroy your ride home.

322
00:16:28,916 --> 00:16:30,750
走着瞧
You will see.

323
00:16:30,785 --> 00:16:33,152
