You will all be stuck here

324
00:16:33,187 --> 00:16:36,923
乞求博克斯在他的餐厅留个工作岗位给自己
begging Borkus for a job in his diner.

325
00:16:36,957 --> 00:16:39,959


326
00:16:58,213 --> 00:17:00,982
OK,让我们瞧瞧我们面对的是什么
Okay, let's see what we're up against.

327
00:17:01,050 --> 00:17:02,050
Gregor.

328
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:09,823
等一下，那儿
Wait.
There.

329
00:17:09,858 --> 00:17:12,059
有一艘巡洋舰在那边
There's a cruiser up there.

330
00:17:12,093 --> 00:17:13,694
