And that shuttle, I think--

331
00:17:13,728 --> 00:17:17,530
是的，它正在装运矿物Rhydonium
Yes, it's being loaded up
with Rhydonium canisters.

332
00:17:19,934 --> 00:17:20,901
Huh.

333
00:17:20,935 --> 00:17:22,069
我想博克斯先生
I guess Mr. Borkus

334
00:17:22,103 --> 00:17:24,704
实际上没有说谎，至少这次如此
was actually telling
the truth...for once.

335
00:17:24,739 --> 00:17:27,005
Rhydonium是什么矿物？
What exactly is Rhydonium?

336
00:17:27,039 --> 00:17:28,439
