It's a fuel.

337
00:17:28,474 --> 00:17:30,708
大部分产自ABAFAR这里
Mostly been mined out on Abafar.

338
00:17:30,742 --> 00:17:32,409
极不稳定，而且危险
It's volatile and dangerous.

339
00:17:32,443 --> 00:17:34,577


340
00:17:34,612 --> 00:17:37,412
是的，现在我们有一个新任务：
Yes, we do have a new mission:

341
00:17:37,447 --> 00:17:41,149
阻止分离势力炸毁那艘巡逻舰
Stop the Separatists
from blowing up that cruiser.

342
00:17:41,183 --> 00:17:42,917
