I'll cover you
and clear the way, Colonel.

343
00:17:42,951 --> 00:17:44,451
你们所有人直接冲上飞船
You all head straight to the shuttle.

344
00:17:44,519 --> 00:17:46,253
我来对付那些铁皮人
I'll take care of those clankers.

345
00:17:46,287 --> 00:17:48,955
嗯，听起来像个好计划
Hmm, sounds like a good plan.

346
00:17:48,990 --> 00:17:51,691
你的士兵准备浴血奋战了吗？
You soldiers ready to get dangerous?

347
00:17:51,725 --> 00:17:54,626


348
00:17:56,162 --> 00:17:58,462
