I'll meet you at the shuttle, sir.

349
00:17:58,496 --> 00:18:00,430
我们出发
Let's roll.

350
00:18:07,103 --> 00:18:08,537
Hey!

351
00:18:10,806 --> 00:18:14,442
你需要授权进入这个区域
You need authorization
to enter this area.

352
00:18:14,476 --> 00:18:15,443
Agh!

353
00:18:17,646 --> 00:18:18,612
消灭他们！
Get them!

354
00:18:20,648 --> 00:18:21,782
Agh!

355
00:18:36,596 --> 00:18:38,330
干得好，Gregor.
Good job, Gregor.

356
00:18:44,569 --> 00:18:46,570
看，他在那里！
Look, he's up there!

357
00:18:54,811 --> 00:18:56,378
继续前进
Just keep moving.

358
00:18:56,412 --> 00:18:57,646
一切尽在控制中
It is all under control.

359
00:19:04,954 --> 00:19:08,289
