Colonel, can you hear me?

364
00:19:23,104 --> 00:19:25,205
自求多福！
Save yourselves!

365
00:19:25,239 --> 00:19:27,040
Okay.
Whoa!

366
00:19:27,074 --> 00:19:28,041
Agh!

367
00:19:28,075 --> 00:19:30,643
Whoa-oh-oh.

368
00:19:30,677 --> 00:19:33,645
[blasters firing]

369
00:19:40,686 --> 00:19:43,154
每个人都到这了吗？
Did everybody make it?

370
00:19:43,188 --> 00:19:45,690
不，铁皮人和上校还在外面
No, Beezee and the colonel
are still out there.

371
00:19:45,724 --> 00:19:48,025
