I'll never make it back alive.

375
00:20:00,005 --> 00:20:01,406
不，你可以的，先生
Yes, you will, sir.

376
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,940
我天生就注定要这样
This is what I was born to do.

377
00:20:02,975 --> 00:20:04,709
快,趁现在还不晚
Now, go before it's too late.

378
00:20:27,530 --> 00:20:29,398
我很高兴能和你一起战斗，上校
It's been an honor
serving with you, Colonel.

379
00:20:32,368 --> 00:20:33,569
R2说得对
Artoo's right.

380
00:20:33,603 --> 00:20:35,771
