We can swing back around
and pick you up.

381
00:20:35,806 --> 00:20:38,474
别担心我
Don't worry about me.

382
00:20:38,508 --> 00:20:40,409
你让我记得我是谁
You made me remember who I am.

383
00:20:40,443 --> 00:20:42,244
我发誓，我会回家的
I'll make my way home.
I promise.

384
00:20:42,279 --> 00:20:43,412
现在，出发！
Now go!

385
